# API Examples - POC Sumsub Integration
# Usa este archivo con la extensión REST Client de VS Code o similares

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@externalUserId = emp-co-001

### ==============================================
### SUMSUB API ENDPOINTS
### ==============================================

### 1. Crear Applicant (Empresa Colombia 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/applicants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "externalUserId": "emp-co-001",
  "levelName": "kyb-latam-colombia",
  "companyName": "Empresa Colombia 1",
  "country": "CO"
}

### 2. Crear Applicant (Empresa Colombia 2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/applicants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "externalUserId": "emp-co-002",
  "levelName": "kyb-latam-colombia",
  "companyName": "Empresa Colombia 2",
  "country": "CO"
}

### 3. Crear Applicant (Empresa Brasil 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/applicants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "externalUserId": "emp-br-001",
  "levelName": "kyb-latam-brazil",
  "companyName": "Empresa Brasil 1",
  "country": "BR"
}

### 4. Generar Permalink (Colombia 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/permalinks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "externalUserId": "emp-co-001",
  "levelName": "kyb-latam-colombia",
  "ttl": 86400
}

### 5. Generar Permalink (Colombia 2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/permalinks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "externalUserId": "emp-co-002",
  "levelName": "kyb-latam-colombia",
  "ttl": 86400
}

### 6. Generar Permalink (Brasil 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/permalinks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "externalUserId": "emp-br-001",
  "levelName": "kyb-latam-brazil",
  "ttl": 86400
}

### 7. Obtener Applicant por External User ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/applicants/{{externalUserId}}

### 8. Obtener Level por País (Colombia)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/levels/CO

### 9. Obtener Level por País (Brasil)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/levels/BR

### 10. Obtener Level por País (México)
GET {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/levels/MX

### ==============================================
### WEBHOOK ENDPOINTS
### ==============================================

### 11. Test Webhook (Sin validación de firma)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/sumsub/test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicantId": "test-123",
  "externalUserId": "emp-co-001",
  "type": "applicantCreated",
  "reviewStatus": "init"
}

### 12. Test Webhook - Applicant Pending
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/sumsub/test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicantId": "test-123",
  "inspectionId": "inspection-456",
  "correlationId": "correlation-789",
  "externalUserId": "emp-co-001",
  "type": "applicantPending",
  "reviewStatus": "pending",
  "createdAt": "2024-02-24T10:00:00Z"
}

### 13. Test Webhook - Applicant Reviewed (Approved)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/sumsub/test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicantId": "test-123",
  "inspectionId": "inspection-456",
  "correlationId": "correlation-789",
  "externalUserId": "emp-co-001",
  "type": "applicantReviewed",
  "reviewStatus": "completed",
  "createdAt": "2024-02-24T10:00:00Z",
  "reviewResult": {
    "reviewAnswer": "GREEN",
    "moderationComment": "All documents verified successfully"
  }
}

### 14. Test Webhook - Applicant Reviewed (Rejected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/sumsub/test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicantId": "test-123",
  "inspectionId": "inspection-456",
  "correlationId": "correlation-789",
  "externalUserId": "emp-co-001",
  "type": "applicantReviewed",
  "reviewStatus": "completed",
  "createdAt": "2024-02-24T10:00:00Z",
  "reviewResult": {
    "reviewAnswer": "RED",
    "rejectLabels": ["FRAUDULENT_PATTERNS", "DOCUMENT_TEMPLATE"],
    "moderationComment": "Documents appear to be fraudulent"
  }
}

### ==============================================
### FLUJO COMPLETO DE EJEMPLO
### ==============================================

### Paso 1: Crear Applicant
POST {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/applicants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "externalUserId": "emp-co-test",
  "levelName": "kyb-latam-colombia",
  "companyName": "Empresa Test Colombia",
  "country": "CO"
}

### Paso 2: Generar Permalink
POST {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/permalinks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "externalUserId": "emp-co-test",
  "levelName": "kyb-latam-colombia",
  "ttl": 86400
}

### Paso 3: Verificar Status del Applicant
GET {{baseUrl}}/sumsub/applicants/emp-co-test

### ==============================================
### NOTAS
### ==============================================

# 1. External User ID:
#    - Debe ser único por empresa
#    - Formato recomendado: emp-{country}-{number}
#    - Es permanente y reutilizable

# 2. Levels por País:
#    - Colombia: kyb-latam-colombia
#    - Brasil: kyb-latam-brazil
#    - México: kyb-latam-mexico

# 3. TTL del Permalink:
#    - Por defecto: 86400 segundos (24 horas)
#    - Recomendado: 86400 (24 horas)

# 4. Webhook Signature:
#    - El endpoint /webhooks/sumsub requiere firma válida
#    - Usa /webhooks/sumsub/test para pruebas sin firma

# 5. Review Answers:
#    - GREEN: Aprobado
#    - RED: Rechazado
#    - YELLOW: Revisión manual requerida
